      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipeline",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipeline.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Entry point for building a generic, format-agnostic ETL pipeline. Obtain a fresh builder with\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipeline.Create\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, start from a source — either a built-in <code>From</code> factory (see\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipelineSourceExtensions\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>) or a format-specific factory hung off the\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipeline\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> instance by a format package — append transformer stages on\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipeline%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, terminate with a sink, then call\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipelineSink.RunAsync(System.IProgress%7bWolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipelineProgress%7d%2cSystem.Threading.CancellationToken)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipelineProgress.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipelineProgress.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipelineProgress",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipelineProgress.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An immutable snapshot of a generic <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipeline\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> run's throughput, reported through\nthe <xref href=\"System.IProgress%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> sink passed to\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipelineSink.RunAsync(System.IProgress%7bWolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipelineProgress%7d%2cSystem.Threading.CancellationToken)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipelineSinkExtensions.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
