      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipelineSinkExtensions.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Extensions for terminal <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipelineSink\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> pipelines.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.EtlPipelineSourceExtensions.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
