      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipeline<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipeline-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A generic, format-agnostic ETL pipeline carrying a stream of items of type\n<code class=\"typeparamref\">T</code>. Append transformer stages with <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipeline%601.Through%60%601(Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.ITransformAsync%7b%600%2c%60%600%7d)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>,\nthen terminate with <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipeline%601.To%60%601(Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.LoaderBase%7b%600%2c%60%600%7d)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> (or a format-specific\nsink terminator) to obtain a runnable <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipelineSink\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipelineSink.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipelineSink.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipelineSink",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipelineSink.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A terminated, runnable generic ETL pipeline. Obtained from\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IEtlPipeline%601.To%60%601(Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.LoaderBase%7b%600%2c%60%600%7d)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> or a format-specific sink\nterminator (for example a <code>CsvLoader</code> extension shipped by a format package).</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IExtractAsync-1.yml",
