      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IExtractAsync<TSource>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IExtractAsync-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Defines an asynchronous extractor interface for extracting data of type T.\nA class implementing this interface is intended to be the first step in an\nETL (Extract, Transform, Load) process.</p>\n"
    },
    {
