      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IExtractStageWithProgress<TSource, TProgress>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IExtractStageWithProgress-2.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IExtractStage%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> whose underlying extractor also supports progress\nreporting. Call <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.IExtractStageWithProgress%602.WithProgress(System.IProgress%7b%601%7d)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to supply an <xref href=\"System.IProgress%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nsink that will be forwarded to the extractor's <code>ExtractAsync</code> overload when the\npipeline runs.</p>\n"
